{"lemma":"رِحْلَةٌ","slug":"رِحْلَةٌ","root":"ر.ح.ل","root_slug":"ر-ح-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/ر-ح-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"رِحْلَة","root":"رحل","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":4},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n15054"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%AD%D9%92%D9%84%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"trip, voyage, tour"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"travel, journey","examples":[{"text":"أَنَا مُتَحَمِّسٌ لِبَدْءِ رِحْلَتِيْ إِلَى الجِبالِ الشّاهِقَةِ .","english":"I am excited to start my journey to the towering mountains"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"travelogue"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"destination"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare رَحَلَ (raḥala, “to depart”)."},"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n15054","headword_ar":"رِحْلَةٌ","root":"rHl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act of saddling"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels: (K, * TA:) [and also, agreeably with analogy,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a mode,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner, of saddling"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels:] so in the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu laHasanu Alr~iHolapi","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ لَحَسَنُ الرِّحْلَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is good in respect of the saddling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the mode"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manner of saddling,"},{"kind":"text","text":"of camels]. (K.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A removal, departure,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, S, Msb, K;) and so ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHolapN","text_ar":"رُحْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Lh, Msb, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raHiylN","text_ar":"رَحِيلٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, K: [the last said in the Msb to be and inf. n.:]) you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"danato","text_ar":"دَنَتْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHolatunaA","text_ar":"رِحْلَتُنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qarubato riHolatunaA","text_ar":"قَرُبَتْ رِحْلَتُنَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb) ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Our removal,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"drew near,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has drawn near"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_in~ahu","text_ar":"اـِنَّهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"la*uw riHolapK A_ilaY Almuluwki","text_ar":"لَذُو رِحْلَةٍ اـِلَى المُلُوكِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHolap","text_ar":"رِحْلَة","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Verily he is one who journeys,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"has journeyed, to the kings:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lh, TA:) and in like manner"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHolapN","text_ar":"رُحْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is used in the Kur cvi. 2: (TA:) ―         -b3-  or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riHolapN","text_ar":"رِحْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"with damm, (S, Msb, K,) signifies The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"thing to which one removes, departs,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journeys;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AZ, Msb;) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"direction,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object, to which one desires to repair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"betakes himself:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(AA, S, Msb, K:) and also, (K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHolapN","text_ar":"رُحْلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a single journey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) as ISd says: (TA:) you say, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mak~apu ruHolatiY","text_ar":"مَكَّةُ رُحْلَتِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mekkeh is the point,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"object, to which I desire to remove,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anotumo ruHolatiY","text_ar":"اَنْتُمْ رُحْلَتِى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Ye are they to whom I remove,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"depart,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"journey:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^anota ruHolatunaA","text_ar":"اَنْتَ رُحْلَتُنَا","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Thou art the object to which we repair,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"betake ourselves."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) And hence ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ruHolapN","text_ar":"رُحْلَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is applied to signify"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A noble,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an exalted, person,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a great man of learning, to whom one journeys for his"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the latter's"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"need,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"want, or for his"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the former's"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"science."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b4-  See also the next preceding paragraph, in three places."}],"source_refs":["Lh","Msb","K","S","TA","AA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}